<% if @resource.class.name == "Designer" %>
	Dear <%= @user.full_name %>
	Welcome on board! Thank you for signing up with Custumise and becoming a part of our endeavour to make custom made outfits a part of every woman’s wardrobe. You can now setup your store and add your products. A few simple tips before you get started.
	Try to upload multiple images for the garments like front, side and detail zoom in.
	Give a detailed description about the product in terms of styling, fabric and work.
	Also provide any additional information like dry clean only, do not iron on print etc

	Click the link below to verify your account and get started.

	https://limitless-brook-27912.herokuapp.com/<%= @path %>/confirm/<%= @token %>

	For any information or feedback, email us at connect.custumise.com

	Thank you
	Regards
	Team Custumise
<% elsif @resource.class.name == "User"%>
	Dear <%= @user.full_name %>
	Welcome on board! Thank you for signing up with Custumise. You are only a few steps away from your very own custom made outfit. A few simple tips before you get started on how easy it is to use Custumise.
	Create a request by uploading a picture/s of something similar to what you’re looking for. Write a short description and your budget estimate.
	The designers will send you multiple options based on your request and budget.
	Pick an offer that you like and confirm order by paying online.
	You will have the desired outfit delivered to you right at your doorstep.
	Having some issue? Just contact the designer through the chat or our support team. We will help you with all your needs.

	For any information or feedback, email us at connect.custumise.com

	Thank you
	Regards
	Team Custumise
<% else %>
	Welcome to Custumise. Happy to have you onboard.
<% end %>